<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>肺部感染性疾病 on Aloha's Blog</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</link><description>Recent content in 肺部感染性疾病 on Aloha's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 06 Nov 2022 16:39:10 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>肺炎链球菌肺炎</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E9%93%BE%E7%90%83%E8%8F%8C%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 14:43:32 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E9%93%BE%E7%90%83%E8%8F%8C%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E7%BB%86%E8%8F%8C/%E5%8C%96%E8%84%93%E6%80%A7%E7%BB%86%E8%8F%8C/#肺炎链球菌" class="page" >&lt;strong>肺炎链球菌&lt;/strong>&lt;/a>（SP）（或称肺炎球菌）为 G&lt;sup>+&lt;/sup> 球菌，有&lt;strong>荚膜&lt;/strong>，其毒力大小与荚膜中的多糖结构及含量有关。肺炎链球菌肺炎约占 &lt;a href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/#肺炎的流行病学" class="page" >CAP&lt;/a> 的 50%。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>葡萄球菌肺炎</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%90%83%E8%8F%8C%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 16:00:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%90%83%E8%8F%8C%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E7%BB%86%E8%8F%8C/%E5%8C%96%E8%84%93%E6%80%A7%E7%BB%86%E8%8F%8C/#葡萄球菌" class="page" >&lt;strong>葡萄球菌&lt;/strong>&lt;/a>为 G&lt;sup>+&lt;/sup> 球菌，可分为凝固酶阳性的葡萄球菌（主要为金黄色葡萄球菌）和凝固酶阴性的葡萄球菌（如表皮葡萄球菌、腐生葡萄球菌等）。&lt;strong>金黄色葡萄球菌&lt;/strong>凝固酶为阳性，是化脓性感染的主要原因。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>肺炎克雷伯杆菌肺炎</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%85%8B%E9%9B%B7%E4%BC%AF%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 16:58:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%85%8B%E9%9B%B7%E4%BC%AF%E6%9D%86%E8%8F%8C%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</guid><description/></item><item><title>军团菌肺炎</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%86%9B%E5%9B%A2%E8%8F%8C%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 18:29:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E5%86%9B%E5%9B%A2%E8%8F%8C%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</guid><description>临床表现和辅助检查 症状和体征：高热但相对缓脉，肌痛 X 线征象：斑片状（小片状）浸润，下叶常见；进展迅速；无空洞（主要影响肺泡和细支气管，与小叶</description></item><item><title>肺炎支原体肺炎</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%94%AF%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 18:29:06 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%94%AF%E5%8E%9F%E4%BD%93%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>肺炎支原体肺炎&lt;/strong>是由肺炎支原体（Mycoplasma Pneumoniae，ΜP）引起的呼吸道、肺部（间质性肺炎）的急性炎症改变，常同时有咽炎、支气管炎和肺炎。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>病毒性肺炎</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 18:30:21 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
&lt;dt>病毒性肺炎（viral pneumonia）&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>由病毒侵入呼吸道上皮及肺泡上皮细胞引起的肺间质及实质性炎症。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl></description></item><item><title>肺脓肿</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E8%84%93%E8%82%BF/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 13:53:30 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E8%84%93%E8%82%BF/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
&lt;dt>肺脓肿（lung abscess）&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>是由多种病原体所引起的肺组织化脓性病变，早期为化脓性肺炎，继而坏死、液化，脓肿形成。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl></description></item></channel></rss>